1
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:27,120
Yu Han

2
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:29,160
Li Jing

3
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,400
I knew you would return

4
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:50,880
I...

5
00:00:51,800 --> 00:00:52,960
I originally...

6
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:54,720
I thought

7
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:55,960
I would never see you again

8
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:57,560
That won't happen

9
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:59,040
If you do not come

10
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,040
I will wait forever

11
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:05,720
By the way

12
00:01:05,720 --> 00:01:06,600
I brought you

13
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:07,800
a secret weapon

14
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:09,840
With this secret weapon

15
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:11,560
we can surely repel the Sea Clan

16
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:34,840
I have awaited you here for quite some time

17
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,080
Today

18
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:38,480
none shall escape

19
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:40,320
Minions

20
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:42,200
Seize back the Dragon Pivot

21
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,440
Oh no

22
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,680
The Mystical Bird is here

23
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:10,760
Run quickly

24
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:38,640
I am the Mystical Bird

25
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:41,960
The very Mystical Bird that birthed Shang

26
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,360
That's right

27
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,600
The Great Shang's Guardian Beast

28
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:48,800
Heard you folks were in a bind

29
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,200
So I came to lend a hand

30
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:55,440
This here is my Sacred Plume

31
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,480
Light it up

32
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:58,320
and you can borrow my power

33
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,920
Just a heads-up for ya

34
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:02,840
Unless it's a matter of life and death

35
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,640
don't you light the second one

36
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:07,920
That Dragon Pivot you found

37
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,120
it ain't no ordinary object

38
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:11,760
Long ago, Ancient Emperor Fuxi

39
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,320
used it to stabilize the seas

40
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:15,680
A divine artifact to calm wind and waves

41
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,360
Please enlighten us, Lord Mystical Bird

42
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,480
Why does the Sea Clan seek it so relentlessly?

43
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:23,840
Though the Nine Rivers Dragon Pivot has little power left

44
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,960
that Ao Jiuyuan of the Dragon Clan

45
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:28,040
might just use it to wreak havoc

46
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,000
Dragging all the Nine Provinces

47
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:32,240
into that boundless sea

48
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,680
This is bad

49
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:35,920
The Ninth Prince has an ulterior motive

50
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,400
Do you remember

51
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,640
what the big dragon head said in Guixu?

52
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:42,920
"Descendants of my Dragon Clan bloodline,

53
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:46,160
without the Ancestral Scale's decree,

54
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:49,080
those who dare trespass

55
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:51,800
their blood shall wither,

56
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,680
and their souls shall fall forever."

57
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,600
If the Dragon Clan could not break the seal themselves

58
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:58,480
to retrieve the Dragon Pivot

59
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:00,440
so they used our hands

60
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:01,520
to bring the Dragon Pivot out

61
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,720
So fast

62
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,480
I wonder, compared to the Golden-Winged Roc

63
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:13,560
who is faster

64
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,440
You two stand firm

65
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:18,320
Hold on tight

66
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:36,480
Brother Mystical Bird

67
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,520
thank you

68
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:46,720
Come

69
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,280
look at the gift I brought you

70
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:49,920
I do not recognize these characters

71
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:52,680
Yu Han

72
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,800
Jing'er

73
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,360
Bad news

74
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,160
The Sea Clan army is attacking

75
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,920
How can it be so fast?

76
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:01,520
Just moments ago

77
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:03,800
the sentries we stationed on the island

78
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,880
sent word via carrier pigeon

79
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:07,600
The Sea Clan's army is marching toward Chentang Pass

80
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,720
By tomorrow at the earliest

81
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,120
they will reach the city walls

82
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,680
We lit the beacon before leaving

83
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:27,680
to request aid from Zhaoge

84
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,600
Is there any response?

85
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,800
Jing'er, you are unaware

86
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:33,080
The Zhaoge army

87
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:35,360
has gone north with Grand Preceptor Wen and not returned

88
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,720
How can this be?

89
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:38,000
Not a single soldier

90
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,600
can be dispatched

91
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,320
Could it be

92
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:43,240
the court intends to abandon Chentang Pass to its doom?

93
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:46,800
Quickly summon all the citizens

94
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,040
and all the soldiers

95
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,760
We must not sit and wait for death
